{"tid":2425435,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"存款10厘息剩0.5%恐爆煲 「天下第一村」傳擠提","createTime":"2021-02-27T10:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T11:29:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3ba8d03cac619127f8a9ec1f4623dd37f0d1c0","tid":2425435,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210227/AVQQZU27DBHD3EWZ7BFAEYERHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210227%2FAVQQZU27DBHD3EWZ7BFAEYERHQ%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm1%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=90138055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210227%2FAVQQZU27DBHD3EWZ7BFAEYERHQ%2F&h=0252e009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210227/AVQQZU27DBHD3EWZ7BFAEYERHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n存款10厘息剩0.5%恐爆煲<br />\n「天下第一村」傳擠提<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EtddACd9Qt79ks_9y1Zvc1EqGYU=/2362x1447/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z6GLRPB5UFGI5EJUKITTJ2KKPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEtddACd9Qt79ks_9y1Zvc1EqGYU%3D%2F2362x1447%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ6GLRPB5UFGI5EJUKITTJ2KKPA.jpg&h=3f494eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華西村近年負債纍纍，「天下第一村」風光不再。<br />\n<br />\n農村共同富裕的典型、有「天下第一村」之稱的江蘇華西村，近年被揭負債嚴重，近日更傳出遭擠提。網上有影片顯示，約數百名村民冒雨排隊，有人反映入股時承諾的10%利率，但現時取回時只能按0.5%計算。村民擔心華西村投資失利、取不回款項，連夜晚都排隊。華西村黨委證實影片屬實，澄清只是村民到期取回資金，強調華西資金充足，兌付（還款）沒問題。<br />\n<br />\n「你看取個錢，排隊要排多少人呀！好多人都在排！」............................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8RVxtmDv0Ho9y6BYHlMSZSAFSWc=/919x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/27EC7MSZQFE75IU3GFFYWMZBUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8RVxtmDv0Ho9y6BYHlMSZSAFSWc%3D%2F919x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F27EC7MSZQFE75IU3GFFYWMZBUQ.jpg&h=ad63f108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■網傳華西村擠提場面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數百人連夜冒雨排隊<br />\n<br />\n一名華西村民向本報記者表示，他在2018年存入三萬元人民幣（約3.6萬港元），原本三年後可取30%分紅，即利息連本金可取回3.9萬元(4.67萬港元)。但近日到期後「被華西村賴皮」，利息只得460元，即年息僅約0.5%。被問到集體取款是否因村民擔心爆煲，他稱近年「華西村投資虧損不少，去年本村都沒有分紅」，相信村民是希望早取錢保平安，連夜晚都有人排隊。<br />\n<br />\n華西村黨委發言人證實，影片內容真實，.............................。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/71ttOFvWfjYz6c44NtLQXok8N6k=/586x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FUG7ILH7ZREGBACV6RX5ABWENI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F71ttOFvWfjYz6c44NtLQXok8N6k%3D%2F586x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFUG7ILH7ZREGBACV6RX5ABWENI.jpg&h=c68ffe5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■村民冒雨到華西村辦公樓提款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年負債443億元<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，昔日「中國最富裕村莊」的華西村近年負債纍纍，在2018年第三季度，華西集團總資產達547.6億元人民幣（657億港元），負債369.3億元（443億港元），負債率高達67.4%。<br />\n<br />\n華西村是全國首家以村命名的鄉鎮企業上市公司，旗下控制的公司.....................<br />\n<br />\n在1970年代末改革開放初期，農村推行「家庭聯產承包責任制」，.........................<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/21世紀經濟報道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rIYNKbC6PffQzi0C411XUjHnCag=/749x1230/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6S3WD4CADVAYZORMZXBETJU7N4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrIYNKbC6PffQzi0C411XUjHnCag%3D%2F749x1230%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6S3WD4CADVAYZORMZXBETJU7N4.gif&h=d7a75a36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ab2d33f0a7230d9697808962bb9e6d3f0c38acf","tid":2425435,"uid":42820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"收左美國佬幾多錢搞事呀"},{"pid":"8539394fca5611956058e8518acb0645c5c921b9","tid":2425435,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"天下第一村&hellip;&hellip;負債四百億港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153f2e39e796f96367cca32620a256377dc85c51","tid":2425435,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"有政府唔驚！"},{"pid":"b5da9dbf35b119528ec60ff9c555dfd982f25d21","tid":2425435,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"錢係憑本事拎 點解要還"},{"pid":"d0d43e6c9104b451fd615f22d2e3ee333813aa54","tid":2425435,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"信既人係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddff66ac57b257bae25901403082583859d8432","tid":2425435,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"點解黨委書記要撻老豆個朵？"},{"pid":"b8371f3aa966f1f17f28fea8b73a8c32d1b9e6f6","tid":2425435,"uid":26329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8539394fca5611956058e8518acb0645c5c921b9","tid":2425435,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"天下第一村&hellip;&hellip;負債四百億港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"負債第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c4850fca7a65c469360104406c268f9be4deb1","tid":2425435,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"你post全文出黎<br />\n咁人地唔洗禁入蘋果到睇啦<br />\n<br />\n又唔係hk01,大公文匯"}]}